  "notes": "Route 35 connects Goldenrod City (south) to the National Park area and Route 36 (north). It is 10x18 blocks (20x36 tiles) and features a mix of grass patches, a water channel on the east side accessible via Surf, and 9 trainers. Officer Dirk is night-only. The National Park Gate at the north end manages the Bug-Catching Contest system (Tuesday/Thursday/Saturday). The Goldenrod Gate contains Randy, who initiates the Kenya delivery side-quest. Bug Catcher Arnie's battle dialogue changes when a Yanma swarm is active (ENGINE_YANMA_SWARM flag). The TM04 Rollout item ball sits in the southern grass patch. A fruit tree provides a daily Berry."
}
